data.description: Don't miss this west side charmer on a tree lined cul-de-sac with nearly 2900 square feet, 5 beds (one non conforming) and 3 baths. Listed at less than county appraised value, this home is a great value! The large deck and walk out basement leading to the beautifully landscaped back yard are perfect for entertaining or enjoying nature. The spacious kitchen boasts newer appliances and views over the back yard. On the main floor, you will find the master bedroom with dedicated closet and en suite bath, two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a dining room with french doors leading to the large deck. The cozy finished basement has a family room with fireplace, additional bedroom and bonus non-conforming bedroom/office/bonus room and an additional full bathroom. Contact Laura Ebert at 785-458-9741 to schedule your showing today!
